{"tid":461553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣得一個荃灣谷","createTime":"2017-11-07T16:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T11:12:39.000Z","uid":69260,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3209b3fdd6f0dcc0607881aed621c702a0df0d05","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"大家好呀!好耐冇見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係我地久違了既荃灣谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地荃灣谷招收新朋友仔既時間又到啦~<br />\n首先介紹下荃灣谷先,荃灣谷已經成立左2年啦!<br />\n谷入面聚集一群志同道合,又住係荃葵青一樣既巴打絲打,<br />\n遠至深井葵芳,係群入面已有15+位穩定既成員.<br />\n無論大家係讀緊書定做緊野,結左婚定單身,我地都好歡迎你地既加入.<br />\n中學生哥升學既疑問,揀咩科好~<br />\n爸爸媽媽覺得個仔好鬼難教,寵物應該改咩名好,點樣養最好,<br />\n附近有咩好食,最近開左咩新鋪頭,邊個商場改左名,<br />\n地皇廣場新開既Food Court好唔好食,<br />\n路德圍檔煨蕃薯有冇開,邊間野加左價,<br />\n有咩少男少女心事,同好朋友吵左架,<br />\n毒丁坐小巴最後座唔夠膽大叫有落,唔識點追女仔,<br />\n女仔唔識點比男仔追,少女們男朋友係咪外面有第2個, <br />\n咩開心野傷心野,只要你願意講,就一定有人回應你,<br />\n谷內既哥哥姐姐,叔叔嬸嬸都好樂意比意見你,<br />\n我地荃灣谷既宗旨係希望可以提供一個家庭比大家,<br />\n係入面暢所欲言,放低你既壓力,分享快樂.細水長流.<br />\n<br />\n過去2年既聖誕節,我地荃灣谷都有搞10+人既網聚,<br />\n有得一齊食聖誕大餐,一齊飯後玩遊戲,仲有得抽禮物!<br />\n永不落空,齊齊過個暖笠笠既聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望黎緊呢個2017年既聖誕節可以有你既加入,<br />\n唔好諗咁多啦,Pm我啦,期待你同你,仲有你既加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S.想入荃灣谷既朋友可以係pm入面,<br />\n作簡單既自我介紹,例如係巴打定絲打,<br />\n讀緊書定做緊野,大概年齡同自己既喜好~<br />\n分享你想同我分享既所有事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然唔好忘記留低你既電話號碼啦~<br />\n<br />\n荃灣推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外加多個入group既方法~ <br />\n冇連登帳號既巴絲可以send email過黎呢個email, <br />\n等我加你入黎荃灣大家庭~ <br />\nallintsuenwan@yahoo.com"},{"pid":"84c624396991ac59feb90dc51c0ad19072791172","tid":461553,"uid":1834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"a53ba96781e2fb679861df96e970a76d5c967a97","tid":461553,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:12:08.000Z","msg":"好想join<br />\n但唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8d7241415a7420a12115a5511b66c3c3d9fb33","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"推post大大力"},{"pid":"e6ed3293b57a5ab4eb15f36ac9768d39b9a8acdc","tid":461553,"uid":3333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"連登有帳號都冇得pm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816f53227782d6c5f8b15c802287cbe85a08bfbd","tid":461553,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"有冇telegram呀，好少用email"},{"pid":"4d73ccc794c9909512863080783e67c78aaf4c72","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"冇telegram <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519acc3e2a8adc7e3e366b09d18e2ae9233a4ba2","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"荃灣推"},{"pid":"0f1632e4f582ff8edea055b9800ee80e27cbae33","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"荃灣推推"},{"pid":"cd55792202164fe285e81cbb1bc3000a77f6b79a","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"荃灣推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51082ea3b24ace2de769c6d646ccbb71aaacf116","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"荃灣推推推推"},{"pid":"6fde5d24a389a0f42983c0b08af9b20333e28ed8","tid":461553,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"荃灣推推推推推"},{"pid":"cd0bb9af485500e